            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato & mozzarella tortelloni </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the tortelloni, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
