    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> dried oregano </strong>and<strong> balsamic vinegar</strong> with 80ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[105ml]</span> [130ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
