    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper has softened, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>tomato stock</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce thickens slightly</p>",
