    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained tortelloni </strong>to the sauce with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>sweet pepper & tomato tortelloni</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
